Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:03.98,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:07.60,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.28,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,But to think it was to this extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:28.05,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)\3c&H8ECEDD&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.19,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He's this fast without any cursed energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.72,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the perfected form of Maki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.38,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.33,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Inumaki-senpai, \Nall the normal people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:03.39,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,and transfigured humans are out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.60,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Visualize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.94,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Visualize how to beat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.53,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Visualize winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.20,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Fleeing Hares!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.32,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,That sensation was Sukuna's fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:25.28,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is happening here in Shibuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.26,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He charged through on pure instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.73,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! I no longer have the cursed energy \Nto use Domain Expansion, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.85,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an1\fnArial\bord0\shad0\b1\fs26\pos(30,310)}23:01         Shibuya Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.82,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe, aren't we done \Nwith the interiors yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:40.22,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,They might still be in the veil,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.16,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to Toge, \Neveryone's been evacuated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.48,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,so let's head to Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.29,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,How do we get to floor B5 from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.92,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,Toge said the news about him being \Nsealed is real, so let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.48,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Gojo this, Gojo that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:01.31,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Gojo isn't the only person in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:09.11,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows who might be trembling in \Na nook of Shibuya right this very instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:13.20,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine if it were some young \Nelementary school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.87,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,How would you feel if we overlooked them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.60,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be an \Nexaggeration to say we were
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.45,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,responsible for snuffing \Nout such a bright future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.70,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.09,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, then get to scouring \Nevery building, every floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:28.66,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,and behind all the toilets, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.81,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.34,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running out of room for excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.84,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't want to go near floor B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:40.08,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'd much prefer to wander \Naround like this and waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:42.61,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:47.17,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If Panda knew how to get there, \Nhe'd run off for floor B5 on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.48,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avoid that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.34,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to be \Nleft here alone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:55.85,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a panda, but he has \Nmore of a human heart than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:59.14,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,But because he's a panda, he has no \Nsense of his surroundings here in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.78,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't even noticed that we're \Nalready super close to floor B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.50,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.37,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, be thorough about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.66,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll pretend to be lost \Nin the station next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:13.24,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This huge bundle of cursed \Nenergy keeps appearing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.68,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,and disappearing from \Nthe culprits who sealed Gojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.30,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No way I'm touching that. \NThat would be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.50,Main,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,You're sorcerers from Jujutsu High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.38,Main,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:30.02,Main,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill sorcerers \Nif I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.28,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.17,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,I count three behind him, \Nprobably more in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:43.30,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get murdered, either, \Nbut I can't just roll over and say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.57,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we have a chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.68,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,A nice, long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.16,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The longer this goes, the worse off I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.11,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to risk a short, decisive battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.94,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The one advantage I do have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.68,Main,Shoko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Principal. I have your cursed corpses \Nwith me, so I'll be fine on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:34.97,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,959)\an1\fnArial\bord0\shad0\b1\fs22\pos(30,285)}22:51         Shuto Expressway No. 3 Shibuya Route\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hShibuya Tollbooth
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.35,Main,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You know that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.32,Main,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,The moment they learn about \Nthis place, they'll target it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:42.52,Main,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Satoru is capable of healing others \Nwith his reverse cursed technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.88,Main,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,Ino and Ijichi would both \Nbe dead if you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.72,Main,Shoko,0000,0000,0000,,That was thanks to your \Nquick judgment, Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.68,Main,Shoko,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd waited for Nanami to call for me, \Nwe wouldn't have made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.08,Main,Shoko,0000,0000,0000,,Allowing Nanami to operate freely \Nhas been a major boon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.62,Main,Yaga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had quit smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:06.60,Main,Shoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm recalling the days when \NI was a student for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.86,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,...is that Ieiri-san is close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.42,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay to push my \Nbody further than I should!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.22,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to settle this \Nwith only injuries she can heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.72,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I've narrowed down his paths!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.14,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,But his speed is on par \Nwith Sukuna from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.60,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to follow him by sight! \NJust focus on the timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.23,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,If I mess up the timing, I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.52,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,If I mess up the timing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.24,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.02,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:22.40,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,You know my brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.54,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally got it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:31.48,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind giving him to you once his \Ntechnique becomes clear at age five or six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.93,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how much you'll pay, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.88,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,If he has the hereditary \Ntechnique, I'll take eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.04,Flashback,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll take seven for anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.32,Flashback,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.16,Flashback,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,If he has the hereditary \Ntechnique, I'll pay you ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.96,Flashback_Italics,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that place was a trash dump to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.66,Flashback_Italics,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,it should be much better for \Nhim since he has the talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.22,Flashback_Italics,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.58,Flashback_Italics,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.10,Flashback,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.28,Main,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.99,Main,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.38,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.21,Main,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Zen'in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.27,Main,Toji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.95,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.96,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Enough worrying about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.08,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make haste to Ieiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:01.70,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should make sure Maki-san \Nand the others are safe first...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.70,Main,Shigemo,0000,0000,0000,,See, see? This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.26,Main,Shigemo,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm suited to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.01,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H213835&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.01,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\3c&HA0DCE8&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.70,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperate with that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:25.56,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,You mean for the sake of \Nreclaiming Geto-sama's body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.92,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.63,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,The true identity and goals of \Nthat impostor may be unclear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:34.35,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,but once the world is thrown into chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.34,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,those non-sorcerer monkeys will \Nbe the ones paying the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.48,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Being strong will be necessary for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.12,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,The monkeys will be culled,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.74,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,sorcerers will propagate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.44,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,and cursed spirits will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.85,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,That is the world Geto-sama longed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.88,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.98,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't concern myself with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.00,Flashback,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means \Nto inherit his ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.98,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making this all \Nmixed up and complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.22,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you I won't stay quiet while
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.89,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,the man I loved is being \Nmanipulated like a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:08.25,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Geto-sama's story is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.49,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone taint that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.51,Flashback,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up already, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.36,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,If you start going on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.48,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,about grown-ups and children, \Nthis conversation's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.41,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.76,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:35.29,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing Suguru-chan would want \Nleast of all is for us to hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.98,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you is wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.81,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,So let's agree this is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.46,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,We can each do as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.77,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do, Larue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.77,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.71,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,Same as Miguel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:57.62,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make \NSuguru-chan king, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:01.57,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,But all of you, remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.39,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:10.97,Flashback,Larue,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, somewhere, \Nwe'll all share a meal together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.07,Main,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones carrying \Non the will of Geto-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.77,Main,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,If you're with Jujutsu High,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.42,Main,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,then nothing else needs to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.00,Main,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,Will you surrender or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.40,Main,Suda,0000,0000,0000,,I hate indecisive men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.80,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a panda, so that doesn't apply to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.18,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Their chat was too short, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.81,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Still, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.72,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,With a group on this level?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.43,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:43.32,Italics,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I can take plenty of time just \Nfending them off and dragging this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.09,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,New Shadow Style Iai, Evening Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.09,Main,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.35,Flashback,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is your reward for the fingers. Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.46,Flashback,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to land even \Na single blow on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.49,Flashback,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work under you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:27.26,Flashback,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, how about \NI slaughter every human in Shibuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:30.10,Flashback,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.12,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.87,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.50,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,...cursed spirit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:16.97,Flashback_Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Geto, how strong would you say \NI am in terms of Sukuna's fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.40,Flashback_Italics,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,A generous estimation would be \Nabout eight or nine fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.80,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.88,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.09,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was a gap in our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:23.14,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,But to think it was to this extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.00,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,The moonlight's shining all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.40,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's helping me see your \Npathetic state more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.04,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:53.40,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play along with you again \Nand again until I tire of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.92,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to remain here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.77,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Time to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.98,Main,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.35,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.59,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you curse users!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.89,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but a couple of \Nspecial-grades are fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:17.93,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of elephants are now \Ntap-dancing on top of ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.60,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,And just to be clear, we're the ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.60,Main,Panda,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hurry, hurry, hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.05,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Supreme Art:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.34,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.22,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,New Shadow Style:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.69,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Quick Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.96,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.88,Main,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.40,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:55.91,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby forbid every person in a 100-meter \Nradius from moving until I say "now."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:00.07,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I'll kill anyone \Nwho violates that rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.25,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.42,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Still not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.06,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:37.08,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sukuna shouldn't escape that unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.82,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,If it had hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.58,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you use your domain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:50.94,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't win a \Ntug-of-war between domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.88,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's how it went with Satoru Gojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.89,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's the epitome of a loser's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:03.07,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Though you have managed \Nto pique my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:05.35,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll fight you with your own specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:09.70,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,■, Fuga (Open).
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.94,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.54,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,flames?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.96,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Sukuna's technique \Nwas severing and slicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.85,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I thought it was well-known,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.92,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,but I suppose you wouldn't \Nknow, cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:34.56,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't do anything \Npetty like revealing my technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.30,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Arm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.09,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a contest of firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:16.50,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hanami, Dagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.57,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,There's still Mahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.58,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,Humans fear and loathe death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.74,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the ones standing \Nbehind that are also humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.31,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,To humans, death is a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.49,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,And Mahito is that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:40.95,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,Mahito will continue to grow stronger still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:45.06,Main,Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you placed him \Nat the top of our ranks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:51.40,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll no longer be the same as we \Nare now once we're reborn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:55.75,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Yet even so, I'll eagerly await \Nthe day we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:00.00,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,We are the true humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.16,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,What's this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.37,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to become human?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.99,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:13.88,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to actually be human. \NYou want their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.64,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is that about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.28,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I understand it, that's so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:24.29,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Packs of humans. Packs of curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.18,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,All of you get together and measure \Nyour worth against each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.40,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,driving all of you to grow \Nweaker and stunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:34.10,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You should have burnt everything down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.83,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Burnt everything around you, \Nwithout calculations or plots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:43.07,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Casting aside race, future, everything... \Nuntil you finally reached Satoru Gojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:46.11,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,That hunger to seize your ideals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.18,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,is what you were lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.19,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:59.19,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you managed to entertain me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.18,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I fought humans, sorcerers, \Nand cursed spirits a thousand years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:08.10,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,and you were still one of \Nthe better ones I fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.55,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.81,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You were strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.54,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.44,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.63,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.00,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:43.08,Main,Uraume,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to welcome you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.14,Main,Uraume,0000,0000,0000,,Sukuna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.20,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uraume!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.50,Main,Uraume,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:57.12,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnArial\bord1.5\3a&HE0&\blur1\shad0\b1\fs26\pos(30,310)}23:07         {\fs20}Dogenzaka, In Front of Shibuya 109
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:58.53,Main,Shigemo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.62,Main,Shigemo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:07.01,Main,Shigemo,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, you shitty sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:10.01,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 40\N{\fs30\fscy150}Thunderclap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.78,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Lately I see the Internet talking about \NMentos and soda, but is it really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:44.40,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:47.97,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I happened to eat a Mentos \Nwhile drinking soda at least once when I was kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:50.40,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I don't remember it \Nmeans those videos must be fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.32,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.96,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Thunderclap, Part 2."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:54.99,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Thunderclap, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:54.80,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,See you next week!

